; Regression test for issue #963: find_account_re should find all
; matching accounts, not just the first one.
;
; The old find_account_re returned only the first DFS match.
; The new find_accounts_re (plural) collects every matching account.

2024/01/01 Opening
    Expenses:Food:Groceries    $50.00
    Expenses:Food:Dining       $30.00
    Expenses:Transport         $20.00
    Assets:Cash

; Verify that a regex matching multiple accounts returns them all.
; "Expenses:Food" matches both Expenses:Food:Groceries and
; Expenses:Food:Dining (and the parent Expenses:Food itself).

test bal Expenses:Food
              $80.00  Expenses:Food
              $30.00    Dining
              $50.00    Groceries
--------------------
              $80.00
end test
